    <text id="F0645T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Hover asks his mother to send him a box of supplies.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>
        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient">Mother</name>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        August
                        <name type="place">Camp Near Bel Plain Landing virginia </name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Mother </salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I take my pen in hand to let you <orig reg="know">no</orig> that I am well at
                    this present time and hope that these few lines will find you in the same state
                    of good health. I got the paper and envelopes that you sent me and i was glad to
                    get them for <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> them. I am sorry that John was sick but i am in
                    hope that he will get well again. i think that we will get <orig reg="paid">pade</orig>
                    <orig reg="off">of</orig> in a few days and then i will send some of it home to
                    you i want you to send me a box if you can but if you <orig reg="can't"
                    >cant</orig> it won't make much difference. Direct your box in care of <sic
                        corr="Quartermaster">cortermaster</sic>. Nothing more at the present time
                    but <orig reg="write">rite</orig> soon <del rend="none" hand="h1"/></p>

                <closer>
                    <salute> </salute>
                    <signed>Augustus Hover </signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">i send you my <unclear>
                            <orig reg="old">old</orig>
                        </unclear> likeness But now is <unclear>
                            <orig reg="laterent">laterent</orig>
                        </unclear> round of our <orig reg="Regiment">Righment</orig> and i want you
                        to <orig reg="keep">ke</orig> it till get home and then i will get framed.
                    </seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
